Epammama ya꞉tapo yia꞉ watle epo atlaiyo, “Wua꞉ tamalemama wua꞉ dali ku pohalopo tlowa, epo duli ma pohalopo tlowa, epo daya ma pohalopo tlowa, epo mani ma pohalopo tlowa. Epame sede mape dapiyamte pohalopo tlowa, isikimi hatlo tlo halopo telepe.
