Epame osolo walle oplami Saimon i mape Pilipi yu dla mikadepe depame yú tulupo Pilipi mate sela꞉iyo. Epo sela꞉mama Pilipita ulugiyemale koko halomsela꞉lati natipame ya꞉ sikemte yiyelemsela꞉iyo.
